"the beginning of the game in a world full of darkness and shadow, a small band of rebels fight against a ruthless empire, led by a young revolutionary with visions of a new world. Together they fight a battle for freedom and the future of their people, but will they succeed? the ending of the game through treachery and betrayal, the young revolutionary is captured by the empire and faces a trial of shame. Betrayed by his own people, he is sentenced to death and an uncertain future. Will he survive the trial to face a future of unknown darkness? Will his people ever know freedom? Only time can tell."